id: pm-yvwt
title: Auto-migrate previous-version trackers on first mutation
description: "Current build blocks mutation of 2026.3.12 tracker data until item_format is manually selected, which breaks automatic migration expectations for existing collected data."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[5]: compatibility,migration,pm-cli,release,storage
created_at: "2026-05-01T08:29:05.321Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-01T08:57:23.708Z"
deadline: "2026-05-02T08:29:05.321Z"
author: codex-release-agent
estimated_minutes: 90
acceptance_criteria: "A tracker created by @unbrained/pm-cli 2026.3.12 can be read and mutated by the current build without manual item-format setup; first mutation auto-selects/migrates to the current default format without losing items, linked artifacts, comments, history, or close metadata."
parent: pm-x6ni
resolution: Legacy settings without item_format now auto-select the default format and run pre-mutation item-file migration.
expected_result: Trackers created by @unbrained/pm-cli@2026.3.12 can be read and mutated by the current build without manual item-format setup or data loss.
actual_result: "Previous-version sandbox migrated 3 markdown items to TOON on first current mutation while preserving item count, linked artifacts, comments, close metadata, health, and history integrity."
comments[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-01T08:29:05.321Z",codex-release-agent,"Compatibility sandbox using isolated npm install of @unbrained/pm-cli@2026.3.12 created three legacy items and then current dist/cli.js update failed with exit 4: Write command update requires explicit item format selection before mutations. Duplicate check: pm search 'item format selection before mutations previous version auto migrate' found only closed prior migration feature/task work; pm list-open --type Issue showed no active compatibility issue."
  "2026-05-01T08:36:30.340Z",codex-release-agent,"Implemented compatibility fix: legacy settings without item_format now persist the default item_format and run pre-mutation item-file sync instead of blocking. Evidence: targeted sandboxed integration test passed; previous-version sandbox created 3 items with @unbrained/pm-cli@2026.3.12 and current dist/cli.js migrated 3 .md items to 3 .toon items with item count, linked artifacts, close reason, health, and history drift checks preserved."
